Line numbers are disabled by default, you can enable them by passing the ``lineNumbers`` option to your widget, for example like this:

```
class SomeModelForm(forms.ModelForm):
    class Meta:
        model = SomeModel
        widgets = {'yourfield': CodeMirrorEditor(options={'lineNumbers': True})}
```

As for scroll bars, they should appear once you fill the editor, see the following image:

